description: Supporters of Narendra Modi’s Bharatiya Janata Party celebrated a landslide victory in India’s most populous state on Saturday, consolidating the prime minister’s power and putting him in a strong position to win re-election in 2019.
title: Landslide Victory for Modi’s Party in India
title_page: Landslide Victory for Modi’s Party in India - Video - NYTimes.com
text: Supporters of Narendra Modi’s Bharatiya Janata Party celebrated a landslide victory in India’s most populous state on Saturday, consolidating the prime minister’s power and putting him in a strong position to win re-election in 2019.
